{"tid":147740,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 －櫻花士多啤梨卷(有片睇）","createTime":"2017-03-08T05:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T14:04:39.000Z","uid":30742,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9294548da7139639a1e10ec4f9fa923199e4267f","tid":147740,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H5JgV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH5JgV.jpg&h=f9947e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n士多啤梨又到季尾，加上又差唔多到櫻花季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就將兩者加埋一齊做左個roll cake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加了鹽漬櫻花比單純的草莓卷多了一點咸味，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加埋草莓的酸還有忌廉的甜，口感豐富左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前其實做過幾次roll cake都失敗，唔係蛋糕片焗得唔好就係一卷就裂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個食譜我做左幾次，亦加左唔同變化都相當成功！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有。。重點係。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我終於拍左片喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！雖然就簡陋d，但都cut左我幾日架！<br />\n不過我發現其實剪片都幾好玩既！不過真係好累&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都叫左一個開始啦！ <br />\n<br />\n&lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k7jkrF68-_E&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fk7jkrF68-_E%22&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=da64df3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/embed/k7jkrF68-_E&quot;</a> frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br />\n<br />\n櫻花士多啤梨卷: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/03/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F03%2Fblog-post.html&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=27bb0d85\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/03/blog-post.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cb56c5d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram:  <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=48913faf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=be2e8a99\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"c5e6d65cd3eba74be1184b00eb7787a628de7e31","tid":147740,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"老娘#<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2a9c95467c895794a7136950900f8d09035866","tid":147740,"uid":5448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"支持老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55