0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下次落少少練奶在cream?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會好甜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾滴only... 6, 7滴</blockquote><br />\n重d奶味？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鮮奶油，厚feel"},{"pid":"aa4144f47eaf2f75dcd51954176f3772cce424f1","tid":147740,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘都不斷學/試新野 果然活到老學到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 有冇方法可以整圓身d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講個卷？其實我早左拎出雪櫃～所以扁左少少～再雪實d就會圓d～<br />\n但我趕住拎番老家比兩老～唔理得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2b594693375e59658b6f5221362d0a2a981427","tid":147740,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘都不斷學/試新野 果然活到老學到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 有冇方法可以整圓身d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我試左好多次～次次都唔得～呢d用最hea既方法反而做到～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都真係幾麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de6583cf56a9602a502995ccbc57bf425ee2841","tid":147740,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下次落少少練奶在cream?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會好甜？<img src=\"/a